## Workflow Map

```
Capture Lead Form
    └── Normalize & Pass Lead Data
            └── Required Fields Present?
                    ├── NO  → Log Invalid Lead → Log Unqualified Lead (Sheets)
                    └── YES → Human Buffer → AI Agent (Gemini + Think + Memory)
                                    └── Extract AI Output
                                            └── Switch (High / Nurture / Cold)
                                                    ├── High Intent → Auto-Reply → Append Sheet
                                                    ├── Nurture    → Auto-Reply → Append Sheet
                                                    └── Cold       → Polite Decline → Append Sheet

                                            └── Team Alert → Allow Sheet Sync → Slack Alert

Error Trigger → Slack Alert → Gmail Error Alert
```

